name: "Gatos of Galactica" - Galactible™ #13
description: Holy Felines! You’ve discovered Galactible™ #13,  the “Gatos of Galactica!” Collect this little furry travel companion to assist you in navigating the Galactiverse! This kittay DJs on command, gets you into any club, and sends out positive vibes to help you snap out of any funk! Your Mana has been raised by +2,000,000 bits! Comes with a custom beat made by Pyramid Guy! Galactibles™ are one-of-a-kind and minted as 1-of-1. Only 99 will be made! New Galactibles™ drop every week (sorta) on twitter, so give us a follow @Galactibles!
